Public Remarks: FABULOUS single story home in desirable Warner Ranch Subdivision! Specious 4 bed/2bath, split floor plan with island in Kitchen. 18 inch Tile flooring  in all the right places and plush carpet in bedrooms and vaulted ceilings throughout. Large owner's suite has its own private exit to lovely backyard,   a large bathroom with a garden tub and walk-in closet. Fireplace in Family room.  Backyard has a storage shed, can be used as kids play house or a work area. Built in Garage cabinets. New Roof 2017, AC Heat Pump-2021, Epoxy garage floor 2022, Microwave 2020, extended covered patio 2015.   Kyrene School district. Warner Ranch offers tree-lined streets, two city parks, walking paths, tennis/pickle ball courts and playgrounds, community Pool and Spa!! Central location.Close to 101, 10 and 202.
Private Rmks - DND2: Showings to begin at 10am Friday, April 1.  Offers will be reviewed on Monday April 4th.  Sellers require post possession to May 20th. Please consider using First Arizona Title Company. Sandy Saro, 480-385-6522. SSaro@FirstAZTitle.com.   Lock box is located right of front door behind Tree.
